TC1 - Verify user can search a product based on the given search keywords
Given the user has enter the Zalando home page
When the user enters a search keyword in the search bar
Then the user will see the search page with results related to the given search keywords

Preconditions: TC1
TC2 - Verify user can filter search results based on the given filters
Given the user is on the search result page
And the user taps on the filter button
When the user taps on a filter option
Then the user will see the results filtered according to the selected option

Preconditions: TC1
TC3 - Verify user can sort search results based on the given filters
Given the user is on the search result page
And the user taps on the sort button
When the user taps on a sort option
Then the user will see the results sorted according to the selected option

